Challenges#
After going through key ideas and demos of building LLM-centered agents, I start to see a couple common limitations:

Component One: Planning#
A complicated task usually involves many steps. An agent needs to know what they are and plan ahead.
Task Decomposition#

NTM contains two major components, a controller neural network and a memory bank.
Controller: is in charge of executing operations on the memory. It can be any type of neural network, feed-forward or recurrent.","ANSWER: In addition to the central controller, an autonomous agent system also includes a Memory Bank component. This Memory Bank stores data that the Controller neural network uses when executing operations. This feature allows our agents to learn from past experiences and make informed decisions based on their stored knowledge.","In addition to the central controller, an autonomous agent system also includes a Memory Bank component. This Memory Bank stores data that the Controller neural network uses when executing operations. This feature allows our agents to learn from past experiences and make informed decisions based on their stored knowledge."
