nificantly impacted the way the solution generated the answer are
highlighted in bold. When we review solution logs, we see the
highlighting helps users know which terms to change (or remove)
in their question to get a different answer.
Growth of natural language questions – Over time, the per-
cent of queries submitted in the search bar that are expressed as a
natural language question (versus a keyword search) has increased
